articles.title: Taylor Swift's father allegedly punched photographer in face after Australian leg of her Eras Tour ended - CBS News
articles.description: A photographer says Taylor Swift's father punched him in the face after the end of the Australian leg of the pop superstar's Eras Tour.
articles.content:
Melbourne, Australia — A photographer told police he was punched in the face by Taylor Swift's father on the Sydney waterfront on Tuesday, hours after the pop star's Australian tour ended.
